          "date": "2011-11-22 10:27:49.000000000",
          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "ORI-377 debug: changes to help debug logging infrastructure to save stack",
        "message": "ORI-377 debug: changes to help debug logging infrastructure to save stack\n\n - libcfs_debug_vmsg2() to accept libcfs_debug_msg_data structure\n   to replace SUBSYSTEM, __FILE__, __FUNCTION__, __LINE__ and cdls\n   on the stack\n - libcfs_debug_vmsg1() for regular users like CDEBUG() which don't\n   need 2 format strings\n - CDEBUG, RETURN, EXIT, GOTO, CHECK_STACK to init libcfs_debug_msg_data\n\nChange-Id: Id663188f18adbe5059010929fc0b40927e714771\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
